#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module allows you to configure the settings for the trash."
msgstr "Ta modul vam omogoča konfiguracijo nastavitev za smeti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cleanup:"
msgstr "Čiščenje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to allow automatic deletion of files that are older than the "
"value specified. Leave this disabled to <emphasis>not</emphasis> "
"automatically delete any items after a certain timespan. Set the number of "
"days that files can remain in the trash. Any files older than this will be "
"automatically deleted."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, da dovolite samodejno brisanje datotek, ki so starejše od "
"navedene vrednosti. Če pustite to možnost onemogočeno, se nobene datoteke "
"<emphasis>ne</emphasis> bodo izbrisale samodejno po preteku določenega "
"časovnega intervala. Nastavite število dni, kolikor datoteke lahko ostanejo "
"v smeteh. Vse starejše datoteke bodo samodejno izbrisane."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size:"
msgstr "Velikost:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to limit the trash to the maximum amount of disk space that "
"you specify. Otherwise, it will be unlimited."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, da omejite velikost smeti na disku na vrednost, ki jo "
"navedete. V nasprotnem primeru bo velikost smeti neomejena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limit to"
msgstr "Omeji velikost do"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the maximum percent of disk space that will be used for the trash. "
"The calculated amount of disk space that will be allowed for the trash is "
"displayed right of the spinbox."
msgstr ""
"To je maksimalni delež diska, ki bo uporabljen za smeti. Izračunana vrednost "
"prostora na disku, ki bo namenjen smetem, je prikazana desno od okvirčka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Full trash:"
msgstr "Polne smeti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the size limit is reached, the selected action will be performed, "
"either the oldest or biggest files will be deleted automatically or you will "
"be warned."
msgstr ""
"Ko je dosežena najvišja meja velikosti, se bo izvedlo dejanje, ki ga "
"izberete. Ali bodo izbrisane najstarejše ali največje datoteke, ali pa boste "
"le opozorjeni."
